  "original_title": "\u0b86\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bc1\u0bb5 \u0bb5\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf, \u0ba4\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b85\u0baa\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Army soldier's gun in protest, plantations seized",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "During the demonstration held yesterday (13) near the Parliament, the police said that the Ri-56 rifle of an army soldier was confiscated by the demonstrators.",
        "According to the police, an Ri 56 rifle and 2 magazines containing 60 bullets were confiscated from an injured army soldier.",
        "Meanwhile, more than 80 people were injured in the clashes between the demonstrators and the soldiers on Wednesday"
      ],
